import pandas as pd
import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt


data_2021 = data[data['년']=='2021']

pivot_table = data_2021.pivot_table(index='업종대분류',columns='월',values = '카드매출금액',aggfunc='sum')


plt.figure(figsize = (10,6))
sns.heatmap(pivot_table, cmap='YlGnBu',annot=False,cbar=True)

plt.title('2021년 업종대분류별 월별 카드 매출 히트맵')
plt.xlabel('월')
plt.ylabel('업종대분류')

plt.show()

plt.savefig('heatmap_2021.png')
